既課唔代表個市會唔升<br />\n<br />\n反而囤地唔用既收稅就唔同講法 (東北嗰D數以百萬呎計既農地)"},{"pid":"a50aae24432b914bfbb71d14394c2542792577d3","tid":701362,"uid":10101,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"高估左，即係推出對你都無影響啦"},{"pid":"69b521973b8ec163687047527d4d4c2f94fc7a4a","tid":701362,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"好老實最多吉屋既咪係房署囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時低層單位(1/F, 2/F) 係空置<br />\n<br />\n有d 近大馬路, 好嘈, 有d 長期無太陽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75fccb4e34d73c9dd79afceb1e85aa367bc27aa","tid":701362,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"69b521973b8ec163687047527d4d4c2f94fc7a4a","tid":701362,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"好老實最多吉屋既咪係房署囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多時低層單位(1/F, 2/F) 係空置<br />\n<br />\n有d 近大馬路, 好嘈, 有d 長期無太陽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T06:35:31.000Z","msg":"你賣平D 我唔信無人要啦 依家「剛需」咁勁<br />\n唔想平賣 咪交稅囉"},{"pid":"d2052a67c43db0515d9a59e46e0123b59cd745d9","tid":701362,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"如果真係高估囤貨量，咁就唔會好多人受影響啦，仲嘈乜嘢啫？"},{"pid":"da3450458d4b091e039117bb3897d8d0022210cf","tid":701362,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2052a67c43db0515d9a59e46e0123b59cd745d9","tid":701362,"uid":128603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"如果真係高估囤貨量，咁就唔會好多人受影響啦，仲嘈乜嘢啫？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T08:49:19.000Z","msg":"無記錯租畀人都當空置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d272f2961c0bc2514429d1fa57aaf59ceb53f3f","tid":701362,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-